snippet.title: Hidden Expedition Smithsonian Castle Part 1 Journey To The Past No Commentary
snippet.description: Here is your next mission agent, Rick Stamm, the Smithsonian Castle Curator called to HELP about a strange power outage, but when you and Sam arrived at the scene someone also stolen a blueprint for a 19th century time machine, when the culprit is Sarah Jackson and you followed her, you both seemed to travel back to October 4th, 1862 when Abraham Lincoln is the current president, you find yourself when The Smithsonian and HELP are working together and need your future help to save your future, this walkthrough will take you to The Smithsonian Castle past, figure out why Sarah came back to the past and stop the villain from changing the course of the future.
